  <official_title>A Randomized, Phase IIIB, Open-label, Two-arm, Multicenter, comparatiVe Study on Efficacy and Safety of Lipegfilgrastim (Lonquex, TEVA) in Comparison to Pegfilgrastim (Neulasta®, Amgen) in Elderly Patients With Aggressive B Cell Non-HOdgkin Lymphomas at hIgh Risk for R-CHOP-21-inDuced Neutropenia - AVOID Neutropenia</official_title>
