  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of the study is to demonstrate non-inferiority of lipegfilgrastim to
      pegfilgrastim for the duration of severe neutropenia in the first cycle of chemotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
